quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,105,"'ina 'anzalna 'iilayk -ayha alrswl- alquran mshtmla ealaa alhq; ltfsl bayn alnaas jmyeana bima awha allah 'ilyk, wbassark bh, fala takun liladhin ykhwnwn 'anfusahum -bktman alhq- mdafeana eanhum bima aydwh lak min alqawl almkhalf llhqyqt"
  4,106,"watlb min allah taealaa almaghfirat fi jmye ahwalk, 'iina allah taealaa kan ghfwrana liman yarju fadlah wnwal mghfrth, rhymana bh"
  4,107,"wla tdafe ean aladhin ykhwnwn 'anfusahum bmesyt allh. 'iina allah -sbhanh- la yuhibu man eazumat khyanth, wkthr dhnbh"
  4,108,"ysttrwn min alnaas khwfana min atlaehm ealaa 'aemalihim alsyyt, wala ysttrwn min allah taealaa wala ysthywn mnh, wahu ezz shanuh maeahum belmh, matlae ealayhim hin ydbbirwn -lyla- ma la yardaa min alqwl, wakan allah -teala- mhytana bjmye 'aqwalahum wafealhm, la yakhfaa ealayh minha shy'"
  4,109,"ha 'antum -ayha almwmnwn- qad hajajtum ean hwla' alkhayinin lanfshm fi hadhih alhayat aldnya, faman yhajj allah taealaa eanhum yawm albaeth walhsab? wamin dha aladhi yakun ealaa hwla' alkhayinin wakilana yawm alqyam?"
  4,110,"wmn yuqdim ealaa eamal syiy qbyh, 'aw yazlim nafsah biairtikab ma yukhalif hukm allah wshreh, thuma yarjie 'iilaa allah nadmana ealaa ma eml, rajyana mghfrth wstr dhnbh, yajid allah taealaa ghfwrana lh, rhymana bh"
  4,111,"wamin yemd 'iilaa airtikab dhanb fa'iinama yadura bdhlk nafsih whdha, wakan allah taealaa elymana bhqyqt 'amr ebadh, hkymana fima yaqdi bih bayn khlqh"
  4,112,"wmn yaemal khatiyatan bighayr emd, 'aw yrtkb dhnbana mtemdana thuma yaqdhif bima artkbh nfsana bryyt la jnayt lha, faqad thmmal kdhbana wdhnbana byna"